 ZвҶҗPLOTSVG;S;CX;CY;R;I;X;Y;BVIS;PCHARS;VPCHARS;NP;VPNAMES;SX;SY;NM;FMT;A;HX;HY;SR;COL;MDY;M;D;YR;DN;H;AP;LATD;LATM;NS;LONGD;LONGM;EW;MN;TITLE;BN;BI;PAD;TY;LINE;RAH;RAM;DEC;ALT;AZ;MX;MY;SYM;NAMES;ALLCOORD;NB;BV;BNAMES;BCOORD;ILLU;WX;NLEN;ENTRY;J;VHEIGHT;NCOLS;ROW;HDR;PHASE_LINE
вҚқ Generate SVG star map вҖ” stereographic projection centered on zenith
вҚқ Returns a character vector containing a complete SVG document
вҚқ Coordinate system: 2160Г—2160 map with padding and report tables
вҚқ Uses globals: STARCOORD, PLANETCOORD, VE, VP, BRIGHT, STARNAMES, PLANETNAMES
вҚқ              AAE, PHASE, STATEDDAYNO, STATEDTIME, LAT, LONG, PLANETS, PLANETAA
 PADвҶҗ80
 CXвҶҗPAD+1080 вӢ„ CYвҶҗPAD+1080 вӢ„ RвҶҗ1080
 FMTвҶҗ{вҚ•вҢҠ0.5+вҚө}

вҚқ --- Build title ---
 MDYвҶҗJNUINV STATEDDAYNO
 MвҶҗMDY[1] вӢ„ DвҶҗMDY[2] вӢ„ YRвҶҗMDY[3]
 DNвҶҗDAYNAME STATEDDAYNO
 LATDвҶҗвҢҠ|LAT вӢ„ LATMвҶҗвҢҠ0.5+60Г—(|LAT)-LATD
 NSвҶҗ(1+LAT<0)вҠғ'NORTH' 'SOUTH'
 LONGDвҶҗвҢҠ|LONG вӢ„ LONGMвҶҗвҢҠ0.5+60Г—(|LONG)-LONGD
 EWвҶҗ(1+LONG>0)вҠғ'WEST' 'EAST'
 HвҶҗ12|STATEDTIME
 :If H=0 вӢ„ HвҶҗ12 вӢ„ :EndIf
 APвҶҗ(1+STATEDTIME<12)вҠғ'PM' 'AM'
 MNвҶҗвҚ•вҢҠ0.5+60Г—H-вҢҠH
 :If 1=вүўMN вӢ„ MNвҶҗ'0',MN вӢ„ :EndIf
 TITLEвҶҗ'VIEW FROM ',(вҚ•LATD),' DEGREES ',(вҚ•LATM),' MINUTES ',NS
 TITLE,вҶҗ', ',(вҚ•LONGD),' DEGREES ',(вҚ•LONGM),' MINUTES ',EW
 TITLE,вҶҗ', ON ',DN,' ',(вҚ•YR),'/',(вҚ•M),'/',(вҚ•D)
 TITLE,вҶҗ' AT ',(вҚ•вҢҠH),':',MN,' ',AP

вҚқ --- Placeholder SVG header (viewBox height set at end) ---
вҚқ We build body first, then wrap with correct height
 SвҶҗ''

вҚқ --- Background (full size, set at end) ---
вҚқ Placeholder вҖ” will be replaced

вҚқ --- Title ---
 S,вҶҗ'<text class="title" x="',(вҚ•PAD+1080),'" y="',(вҚ•PAD-20),'">',TITLE,'</text>'

вҚқ --- Crosshairs ---
 S,вҶҗ'<g id="crosshairs" stroke="#333" stroke-width="1">'
 S,вҶҗ'<line x1="',(вҚ•PAD),'" y1="',(вҚ•CY),'" x2="',(вҚ•PAD+2160),'" y2="',(вҚ•CY),'"/>'
 S,вҶҗ'<line x1="',(вҚ•CX),'" y1="',(вҚ•PAD),'" x2="',(вҚ•CX),'" y2="',(вҚ•PAD+2160),'"/>'
 S,вҶҗ'</g>'

вҚқ --- Horizon circle ---
 S,вҶҗ'<circle id="horizon" cx="',(вҚ•CX),'" cy="',(вҚ•CY),'" r="',(вҚ•R),'" fill="none" stroke="#555" stroke-width="2"/>'

вҚқ --- Cardinal directions ---
 S,вҶҗ'<text class="cardinal" x="',(вҚ•CX),'" y="',(FMT CY-R-20),'">N</text>'
 S,вҶҗ'<text class="cardinal" x="',(вҚ•CX),'" y="',(FMT CY+R+35),'">S</text>'
 S,вҶҗ'<text class="cardinal" x="',(FMT CX-R-25),'" y="',(вҚ•CY),'">E</text>'
 S,вҶҗ'<text class="cardinal" x="',(FMT CX+R+25),'" y="',(вҚ•CY),'">W</text>'

вҚқ --- Stars ---
 :If 2=вҚҙвҚҙSTARCOORD
   BVISвҶҗVE/BRIGHT
   :For I :In вҚівҠғвҚҙSTARCOORD
     XвҶҗCX+RГ—STARCOORD[I;1]
     YвҶҗCY-RГ—STARCOORD[I;2]
     :If BVIS[I]
       SRвҶҗ8 вӢ„ COLвҶҗ'bright'
     :Else
       SRвҶҗ3 вӢ„ COLвҶҗ'faint'
     :EndIf
     S,вҶҗ'<circle class="',COL,'" cx="',(FMT X),'" cy="',(FMT Y),'" r="',(вҚ•SR),'"/>'
   :EndFor

вҚқ --- Bright star labels ---
   BNвҶҗ(BRIGHTвҲ§VE)/STARNAMES
   BIвҶҗвҚёBVIS
   :For I :In вҚівүўBI
     XвҶҗCX+RГ—STARCOORD[BI[I];1]
     YвҶҗCY-RГ—STARCOORD[BI[I];2]
     NMвҶҗвҠғBN[I]
     S,вҶҗ'<text class="star-label" x="',(FMT X+12),'" y="',(FMT Y-12),'">',NM,'</text>'
   :EndFor
 :EndIf

вҚқ --- Planets ---
 PCHARSвҶҗ(вүўVP)вҶ‘'вҳҫвҳүвҳҝвҷҖвҷӮвҷғвҷ„вӣўвҷҶвҷҮвҳ„'
 VPCHARSвҶҗVP/PCHARS
 NPвҶҗвүўVP
 VPNAMESвҶҗVP/NPвҶ‘PLANETNAMES
 :If 2=вҚҙвҚҙPLANETCOORD
   :For I :In вҚівҠғвҚҙPLANETCOORD
     XвҶҗCX+RГ—PLANETCOORD[I;1]
     YвҶҗCY-RГ—PLANETCOORD[I;2]
     S,вҶҗ'<text class="planet" x="',(FMT X),'" y="',(FMT Y),'">',VPCHARS[I],'</text>'
     S,вҶҗ'<text class="planet-label" x="',(FMT X+20),'" y="',(FMT Y-16),'">',(вҠғVPNAMES[I]),'</text>'
   :EndFor
 :EndIf

вҚқ --- Zenith marker ---
 S,вҶҗ'<circle cx="',(вҚ•CX),'" cy="',(вҚ•CY),'" r="4" fill="none" stroke="#666" stroke-width="1.5"/>'

вҚқ --- Legend ---
 S,вҶҗ'<g class="legend" transform="translate(',(вҚ•PAD+40),',',(вҚ•PAD+2160+10),')">'
 S,вҶҗ'<circle class="bright" cx="0" cy="0" r="8"/><text x="16" y="6">bright</text>'
 S,вҶҗ'<circle class="faint" cx="120" cy="0" r="3"/><text x="130" y="6">faint</text>'
 S,вҶҗ'<circle cx="230" cy="0" r="4" fill="none" stroke="#666" stroke-width="1.5"/><text x="242" y="6">zenith</text>'
 S,вҶҗ'<text x="350" y="6" fill="#555">вҖ” horizon</text>'
 S,вҶҗ'</g>'

вҚқ === PLANET TABLE ===
 TYвҶҗPAD+2160+120
 NPвҶҗвҠғвҚҙPLANETS
 NAMESвҶҗNPвҶ‘PLANETNAMES
 ALLCOORDвҶҗNP 2вҚҙ0
 :If вҲЁ/VP
   ALLCOORD[вҚёVP;]вҶҗPLANETCOORD
 :EndIf

вҚқ Table layout: columns with pixel positions
вҚқ Cols: Symbol+Name | RA h | RA m | Dec | Alt | Az | Map X | Map Y
 S,вҶҗ'<text class="table-header" x="',(вҚ•PAD+1080),'" y="',(вҚ•TY),'">POSITION OF SUN, MOON AND PLANETS</text>'
 TYвҶҗTY+50

вҚқ Column x-positions for planet table
вҚқ TX holds: name, rah, ram, dec, alt, az, mx, my
 S,вҶҗ'<g class="table-text">'

вҚқ Header row
 S,вҶҗ'<text x="',(вҚ•PAD+60),'" y="',(вҚ•TY),'">BODY</text>'
 S,вҶҗ'<text class="table-hdr-r" x="',(вҚ•PAD+340),'" y="',(вҚ•TY),'">RA h</text>'
 S,вҶҗ'<text class="table-hdr-r" x="',(вҚ•PAD+440),'" y="',(вҚ•TY),'">RA m</text>'
 S,вҶҗ'<text class="table-hdr-r" x="',(вҚ•PAD+560),'" y="',(вҚ•TY),'">DEC</text>'
 S,вҶҗ'<text class="table-hdr-r" x="',(вҚ•PAD+680),'" y="',(вҚ•TY),'">ALT</text>'
 S,вҶҗ'<text class="table-hdr-r" x="',(вҚ•PAD+790),'" y="',(вҚ•TY),'">AZ</text>'
 S,вҶҗ'<text class="table-hdr-r" x="',(вҚ•PAD+920),'" y="',(вҚ•TY),'">MAP X</text>'
 S,вҶҗ'<text class="table-hdr-r" x="',(вҚ•PAD+1050),'" y="',(вҚ•TY),'">MAP Y</text>'

вҚқ Header underline
 TYвҶҗTY+8
 S,вҶҗ'<line x1="',(вҚ•PAD+40),'" y1="',(вҚ•TY),'" x2="',(вҚ•PAD+1080),'" y2="',(вҚ•TY),'" stroke="#555" stroke-width="1"/>'
 TYвҶҗTY+32

 :For I :In вҚіNP
   SYMвҶҗ(NPвҶ‘'вҳҫвҳүвҳҝвҷҖвҷӮвҷғвҷ„вӣўвҷҶвҷҮвҳ„')[I]
   RAHвҶҗвҢҠPLANETS[I;1]
   RAMвҶҗвҢҠ0.5+60Г—PLANETS[I;1]-RAH
   DECвҶҗвҢҠ0.5+PLANETS[I;2]
   S,вҶҗ'<text x="',(вҚ•PAD+60),'" y="',(вҚ•TY),'">',SYM,' ',(вҠғNAMES[I]),'</text>'
   S,вҶҗ'<text class="table-r" x="',(вҚ•PAD+340),'" y="',(вҚ•TY),'">',(вҚ•RAH),'</text>'
   S,вҶҗ'<text class="table-r" x="',(вҚ•PAD+440),'" y="',(вҚ•TY),'">',(вҚ•RAM),'</text>'
   S,вҶҗ'<text class="table-r" x="',(вҚ•PAD+560),'" y="',(вҚ•TY),'">',(вҚ•DEC),'</text>'
   :If VP[I]
     ALTвҶҗвҢҠ0.5+PLANETAA[I;1]
     AZвҶҗвҢҠ0.5+PLANETAA[I;2]
     MXвҶҗ0.01Г—вҢҠ0.5+100Г—ALLCOORD[I;1]
     MYвҶҗ0.01Г—вҢҠ0.5+100Г—ALLCOORD[I;2]
     S,вҶҗ'<text class="table-r" x="',(вҚ•PAD+680),'" y="',(вҚ•TY),'">',(вҚ•ALT),'</text>'
     S,вҶҗ'<text class="table-r" x="',(вҚ•PAD+790),'" y="',(вҚ•TY),'">',(вҚ•AZ),'</text>'
     S,вҶҗ'<text class="table-r" x="',(вҚ•PAD+920),'" y="',(вҚ•TY),'">',(вҚ•MX),'</text>'
     S,вҶҗ'<text class="table-r" x="',(вҚ•PAD+1050),'" y="',(вҚ•TY),'">',(вҚ•MY),'</text>'
   :EndIf
   TYвҶҗTY+34
 :EndFor
 S,вҶҗ'</g>'

вҚқ Moon phase line
 TYвҶҗTY+10
 ILLUвҶҗ0.01Г—вҢҠ0.5+100Г—0.5Г—1-COSв—Ӣ2Г—PHASE
 WXвҶҗ(1+PHASE>0.5)вҠғ'WAXING' 'WANING'
 PHASE_LINEвҶҗ'MOON PHASE ',(вҚ•ILLU),' ',WX
 S,вҶҗ'<text class="table-text" x="',(вҚ•PAD+60),'" y="',(вҚ•TY),'">',PHASE_LINE,'</text>'
 TYвҶҗTY+60

вҚқ === BRIGHT STAR TABLE ===
 BVвҶҗBRIGHTвҲ§VE
 NBвҶҗ+/BV
 :If NB>0
   BNAMESвҶҗBV/STARNAMES
   BCOORDвҶҗ(VE/BRIGHT)вҢҝSTARCOORD
   S,вҶҗ'<text class="table-header" x="',(вҚ•PAD+1080),'" y="',(вҚ•TY),'">BRIGHT STARS</text>'
   TYвҶҗTY+50

вҚқ Header row
   S,вҶҗ'<g class="table-text">'
   S,вҶҗ'<text x="',(вҚ•PAD+60),'" y="',(вҚ•TY),'">STAR</text>'
   S,вҶҗ'<text class="table-hdr-r" x="',(вҚ•PAD+340),'" y="',(вҚ•TY),'">ALT</text>'
   S,вҶҗ'<text class="table-hdr-r" x="',(вҚ•PAD+440),'" y="',(вҚ•TY),'">AZ</text>'
   S,вҶҗ'<text class="table-hdr-r" x="',(вҚ•PAD+560),'" y="',(вҚ•TY),'">MAP X</text>'
   S,вҶҗ'<text class="table-hdr-r" x="',(вҚ•PAD+680),'" y="',(вҚ•TY),'">MAP Y</text>'
   TYвҶҗTY+8
   S,вҶҗ'<line x1="',(вҚ•PAD+40),'" y1="',(вҚ•TY),'" x2="',(вҚ•PAD+720),'" y2="',(вҚ•TY),'" stroke="#555" stroke-width="1"/>'
   TYвҶҗTY+32

   :For I :In вҚіNB
     ALTвҶҗвҢҠ0.5+AAE[I;1]
     AZвҶҗвҢҠ0.5+AAE[I;2]
     MXвҶҗ0.01Г—вҢҠ0.5+100Г—BCOORD[I;1]
     MYвҶҗ0.01Г—вҢҠ0.5+100Г—BCOORD[I;2]
     S,вҶҗ'<text x="',(вҚ•PAD+60),'" y="',(вҚ•TY),'">',(вҠғBNAMES[I]),'</text>'
     S,вҶҗ'<text class="table-r" x="',(вҚ•PAD+340),'" y="',(вҚ•TY),'">',(вҚ•ALT),'</text>'
     S,вҶҗ'<text class="table-r" x="',(вҚ•PAD+440),'" y="',(вҚ•TY),'">',(вҚ•AZ),'</text>'
     S,вҶҗ'<text class="table-r" x="',(вҚ•PAD+560),'" y="',(вҚ•TY),'">',(вҚ•MX),'</text>'
     S,вҶҗ'<text class="table-r" x="',(вҚ•PAD+680),'" y="',(вҚ•TY),'">',(вҚ•MY),'</text>'
     TYвҶҗTY+34
   :EndFor
   S,вҶҗ'</g>'
 :EndIf

вҚқ --- Compute final height and wrap ---
 VHEIGHTвҶҗTY+PAD
 ZвҶҗ'<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 ',(вҚ•2160+2Г—PAD),' ',(вҚ•VHEIGHT),'" width="',(вҚ•2160+2Г—PAD),'" height="',(вҚ•VHEIGHT),'">'
 Z,вҶҗ'<defs><style>'
 Z,вҶҗ'text{font-family:monospace;fill:#ccc}'
 Z,вҶҗ'.bright{fill:#ffd700}'
 Z,вҶҗ'.faint{fill:#aaa}'
 Z,вҶҗ'.star-label{font-size:28px;fill:#ffd700}'
 Z,вҶҗ'.planet{fill:#4fc3f7;font-size:36px}'
 Z,вҶҗ'.planet-label{font-size:24px;fill:#4fc3f7}'
 Z,вҶҗ'.cardinal{font-size:40px;fill:#888;text-anchor:middle;dominant-baseline:central}'
 Z,вҶҗ'.legend{font-size:22px;fill:#999}'
 Z,вҶҗ'.title{font-size:26px;fill:#999;text-anchor:middle}'
 Z,вҶҗ'.table-header{font-size:28px;fill:#bbb;text-anchor:middle}'
 Z,вҶҗ'.table-text{font-size:26px;fill:#999}'
 Z,вҶҗ'.table-hdr-r{font-size:26px;fill:#bbb;text-anchor:end}'
 Z,вҶҗ'.table-r{font-size:26px;fill:#999;text-anchor:end}'
 Z,вҶҗ'</style></defs>'
 Z,вҶҗ'<rect width="',(вҚ•2160+2Г—PAD),'" height="',(вҚ•VHEIGHT),'" fill="#0a0a1a"/>'
 Z,вҶҗS
 Z,вҶҗ'</svg>'
